<inglise> of 30 September 1999 fixing the amounts available in 1999 under the special framework of assistance for traditional ACP suppliers of bananas (Council Regulation (EC) No 856/1999) </inglise>
<eesti> KOMISJONI OTSUS 1999/706/E&Uuml;, millega m&auml;&auml;ratakse kindlaks tavap&auml;rastele AKV banaanitarnijatele antava toetuse eriraamistikus (n&otilde;ukogu m&auml;&auml;rus (E&Uuml;) nr 856/1999) 1999. aastal saadaolevad summad 30. september 1999 </eesti>
<inglise> (notified under document number C(1999) 3097) </inglise>
<eesti> (avaldatud numbri K(1999) 3097 all) </eesti>
<inglise> (1999/706/EC) </inglise>
<eesti> EUROOPA &Uuml;HENDUSTE KOMISJON, </eesti>
<inglise> THE COMMISSION OF THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa &Uuml;henduse asutamislepingut, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Community, Having regard to Council Regulation (EC) No 856/1999 of 22 April 1999 establishing a special framework of assistance for traditional ACP suppliers of bananas(1), and in particular Article 7 thereof, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 22. aprilli 1999. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (E&Uuml;) nr 856/1999 tavap&auml;rastele AKV banaanitarnijatele antava toetuse eriraamistiku kehtestamise kohta, (1) eriti selle artiklit 7, ning arvestades, et: </eesti>
<inglise> (1) Whereas Council Regulation (EC) No 856/1999 establishes a special framework for technical and financial assistance to assist traditional ACP suppliers of bananas to adapt to new market conditions following the amendments made to the common market organisation; </inglise>
<eesti> 1) n&otilde;ukogu m&auml;&auml;rusega (E&Uuml;) nr 856/1999 n&auml;hakse ette tehnilise ja rahalise toetuse eriraamistik, et aidata tavap&auml;rastel AKV banaanitarnijatel kohaneda &uuml;hises turukorralduses tehtud muudatustest tulenevate uute turutingimustega; </eesti>
<inglise> (2) Whereas Article 7 of the said Regulation provides for the Commission to fix, on an annual basis, the maximum amount available for each traditional ACP supplier of bananas on the basis of the competitiveness gap observed taking into account the importance of banans for the country concerned; </inglise>
<eesti> 2) k&otilde;nealuse m&auml;&auml;ruse artikliga 7 n&auml;hakse ette, et komisjon peab m&auml;&auml;rama igaks aastaks iga tavap&auml;rase AKV banaanitarnija jaoks saadaoleva maksimumsumma kindlaks konkurentsiv&otilde;imes t&auml;heldatud mahaj&auml;&auml;muse p&otilde;hjal, v&otilde;ttes arvesse banaanide t&auml;htsust asjaomases riigis; </eesti>
<inglise> (3) Whereas Commission Regulation No 1609/1999(2), and in particular Articles 3 and 4 thereof, sets down the precise method for calculating the competitiveness gap observed and the importance of bananas to the ACP country concerned; </inglise>
<eesti> 3) komisjoni m&auml;&auml;ruses (E&Uuml;) nr 1609/1999 (2) ja eriti selle artiklites 3 ja 4 s&auml;testatakse t&auml;pne meetod, kuidas arvutada konkurentsiv&otilde;imes t&auml;heldatud mahaj&auml;&auml;must ja banaanide t&auml;htsust asjaomasele AKV riigile; </eesti>
<inglise> (4) Whereas Article 7 of Commission Regulation No 1609/1999 provides for the Commission to reallocate funds where any traditional ACP supplier has not presented a request for financial and technical assistance within the deadline set out in Article 1(1) of the Regulation or where the programmes presented are not in compliance with the long-term strategy defined in Article 1(2) of the Regulation; </inglise>
<eesti> 4) komisjoni m&auml;&auml;ruse (E&Uuml;) nr 1609/1999 artikliga 7 n&auml;hakse ette, et komisjon peab vahendid &uuml;mber jaotama, kui tavap&auml;rane AKV tarnija ei ole esitanud tehnilise ja rahalise toetuse taotlust k&otilde;nealuse m&auml;&auml;ruse artikli 1 l&otilde;ikes 1 s&auml;testatud t&auml;htajaks v&otilde;i kui esitatud programmid ei vasta k&otilde;nealuse m&auml;&auml;ruse artikli 1 l&otilde;ikes 2 m&auml;&auml;ratletud pikaajalisele strateegiale; </eesti>
<inglise> (5) Whereas the Member responsible for Development is authorised to sign, on behalf of the Commission, a financing agreement for the precise funds concerned by this Decision, </inglise>
<eesti> 5) arendust&ouml;&ouml; eest vastutaval komisjoni liikmel on volitus kirjutada komisjoni nimel alla k&auml;esolevas otsuses s&auml;testatud vahendeid k&auml;sitlevale rahastamislepingule, </eesti>
<inglise> HAS DECIDED AS FOLLOWS: </inglise>
<eesti> ON VASTU V&Otilde;TNUD J&Auml;RGMISE OTSUSE. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 1 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 1 </eesti>
<inglise> The amount of funds available to each traditional ACP supplier will be those as listed in the Annex to this Decision. </inglise>
<eesti> Iga tavap&auml;rase AKV tarnija jaoks saadaolevate vahendite suurus on esitatud k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;ruse lisas. </eesti>
<inglise> These are indicative amounts and do not represent a commitment to the ACP traditional supplier concerned. </inglise>
<eesti> K&otilde;nealused summad on soovituslikud ja ei ole asjaomasele tavap&auml;rasele AKV tarnijale kohustuslikud. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> The Member responsible for Development is authorised, on behalf of the Commission, to reallocate the amounts set down in the Annex to this Decision in compliance with the provisions laid down in Article 7 of Regulation (EC) No 1609/1999. </inglise>
<eesti> Arendust&ouml;&ouml; eest vastutaval komisjoni liikmel on volitus jaotada komisjoni nimel &uuml;mber k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;ruse lisas s&auml;testatud summad m&auml;&auml;ruse (E&Uuml;) nr 1609/1999 artikli 7 s&auml;tete kohaselt. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 3 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 3 </eesti>
<inglise> The Member responsible for Development is authorised to sign, on behalf of the Commission, a financing agreement with each traditional ACP supplier on the precise level of funds to be allocated, on the basis of an annual action plan of investments. </inglise>
<eesti> Arendust&ouml;&ouml; eest vastutaval komisjoni liikmel on volitus kirjutada komisjon nimel alla investeeringuid k&auml;sitleva tegevuskava p&otilde;hjal m&auml;&auml;ratavate vahendite t&auml;pset taset k&auml;sitlevatele rahastamislepingule, mis s&otilde;lmitakse iga tavap&auml;rase AKV tarnijaga. </eesti>
<inglise> Done at Brussels, 30 September 1999. </inglise>
<eesti> Br&uuml;ssel, 30. september 1999 </eesti>
<inglise> For the Commission Poul NIELSON Member of the Commission </inglise>
<eesti> Komisjoni nimel komisjoni liige Poul NIELSON </eesti>
